Class AdjacencyVect

java.lang.Object
DSA.Graphs.MatrixGraph.AdjacencyVect
All Implemented Interfaces:
Iterable<Integer>, Collection<Integer>
public class AdjacencyVect extends Object implements Collection<Integer>
A specialized collection implementation for storing adjacency information in a graph. Uses a boolean array to efficiently store vertex connections.
